<!-- x402 price SoT = src/lib/x402.ts TOOL_PRICING ($0.01 scan_funding_arb · $0.02 get_trade_call · $0.02 get_market_regime, USDC on Base). These are static constants surfaced in the JSON-LD Offers, the pricing card, llms*.txt + signup; update them there + re-render. Manifest-driving them (like the live track-record numbers) is flagged as OPS-X402-PRICE-SOT-W{NEXT}. WEBSITE-X402-SURFACING-W1. -->
