<div class="lp-belowfold-desktop"><section id="core-capabilities" style="position:relative;padding:120px 80px;border-top:1px solid var(--line);background:transparent"><div style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:10px;margin-bottom:18px;font-family:var(--font-mono);font-size:11px;color:var(--fg-3);letter-spacing:0.14em;text-transform:uppercase"><span style="width:5px;height:5px;border-radius:50%;background:var(--accent, var(--mint));box-shadow:0 0 8px var(--accent, var(--mint))"></span>· capabilities</div><h2 style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:48px;line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-0.022em;font-weight:500;margin:0;text-wrap:balance;color:var(--fg)">Core capabilities</h2><p style="font-size:17px;color:var(--fg-2);max-width:600px;margin:20px 0 56px;line-height:1.6">Three MCP tools your agent can call — plus the self-tuning model behind them.<br/>Each returns a single, structured verdict — not raw indicators.</p><div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:22px"><article style="position:relative;padding:32px 32px 28px;border:1px solid var(--line);border-radius:14px;background:oklch(0.18 0.014 265 / 0.55);display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:20px;min-height:220px"><div style="width:52px;height:52px;border-radius:11px;border:1px solid var(--line-2);background:oklch(0.22 0.012 265 / 0.7);display:grid;place-items:center;color:var(--fg)"><svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 32 32" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="4" y="20" width="4" height="8" rx="1"></rect><rect x="11" y="14" width="4" height="14" rx="1"></rect><rect x="18" y="9" width="4" height="19" rx="1"></rect><path d="M5 11l8 4 5-3 7 4" stroke="var(--accent, oklch(0.86 0.16 165))" stroke-width="1.5"></path><path d="M22 6h4v4" stroke="var(--accent, oklch(0.86 0.16 165))"></path></svg></div><div><div style="font-family:var(--font-display);font-size:23px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:-0.012em;margin-bot